text: Erik Olsson (14 January 1930 - 12 January 2016) was a Swedish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman featherweight at the 1964 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:2016 deaths Category:Swedish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Sweden Category:Wrestlers at the 1964 Summer Olympics Category:People from Kristianstad Municipality
